article_metadata.title: At least 1,000 are expected to attend free health clinic Saturday at Bartle Hall | The Kansas City Star

og.description: A similar two-day clinic at Bartle Hall in December 2009 drew more than 2,000 people. Some patients were diagnosed with dangerously high blood pressure. Others had pneumonia. At least one was rushed to an emergency room with a possible heart attack.
